{{Vgname|憤怒鳥史黛拉|en=Angry Birds Stella|cn=愤怒的小鸟思黛拉|tw=憤怒鳥史黛拉}}是[[Rovio娛樂|Rovio娛樂]]開發的休閒[[益智遊戲|益智遊戲]]，於2014年公佈，這是[[愤怒的小鸟系列|憤怒鳥系列]]中第二款衍生出來的遊戲。本款遊戲主角為[[愤怒的小鸟_(游戏)|憤怒鳥]]其中之一角色粉紅鳥（或稱史黛拉），其餘遊戲角色幾乎是女性角色，Rovio行銷長Blanca Juti對此解釋道，此款遊戲並非是針對女性玩家所設計的遊戲，而是要改變性別刻板印象。<ref>{{cite web |last=Rossi |first=Juhana |url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303417104579546104176570972?mg=reno64-wsj&url=http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB10001424052702303417104579546104176570972.html |title=Boss Talk: Angry Birds Maker Rovio Aims for the Next Level - WSJ.com |publisher=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] |date=2014-05-06 |accessdate=2014-05-13 |archive-date=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511120130/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303417104579546104176570972?mg=reno64-wsj&url=http%3A%2F%2Fonline.wsj.com%2Farticle%2FSB10001424052702303417104579546104176570972.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bnext.com.tw/article/view/id/33665 |title=Rovio新作憤怒鳥史黛拉，顛覆性別刻板印象 |publisher=數位時代 |date=2014-09-04 |accessdate=2015-09-05 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923192857/http://www.bnext.com.tw/article/view/id/33665 |dead-url=no }}</ref>Rovio在2014年2月13日宣布，將會發行與憤怒鳥史黛拉相關的電視影片及相關遊戲專屬Telepod商品。<ref>{{cite web |author=Rovio Announces ‘Angry Birds Transformers’ |url=http://www.morningnewsusa.com/rovio-announces-angry-birds-transformers-2310615.html |title=Rovio Announces ‘Angry Birds Transformers’ |publisher=Morning News USA |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624144643/http://www.morningnewsusa.com/rovio-announces-angry-birds-transformers-2310615.html |archive-date=2014-06-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Angry Birds Stella Launches in the Fall, Introduces Five New Bird Types|url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/Angry-Birds-Stella-Launches-in-the-Fall-Introduces-Five-New-Bird-Types-426600.shtml|author=Andrei Dumitrescu|work=Sof