=== 卡通 ===

Rovio宣布將以此款遊戲為基準，於2014年11月發行卡通，該卡通名為《'''憤怒鳥史黛拉'''》，首集於2014年11月1日發行。<ref>{{cite web|title=Angry Birds Stella Animated Series!|url=https://www.angrybirds.com/blog/angry-birds-stella-animated-series|publisher=Angry Birds|date=|accessdate=October 4, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192621/https://www.angrybirds.com/blog/angry-birds-stella-animated-series|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Angry Birds Stella Animated Series Exclusive Premiere!|url=https://www.angrybirds.com/blog/stella-animated-series-exclusive-premiere|publisher=Angry Birds|date=|accessdate=November 1, 2014|archive-date=2015-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329233520/https://www.angrybirds.com/blog/stella-animated-series-exclusive-premiere|dead-url=no}}</ref>與[[憤怒鳥卡通|憤怒鳥卡通]]相同，動畫時間約6分鐘，片中沒有對話，只有面部表情、聲音效果與簡單的發聲。在卡通劇情中，會介紹史黛拉的好友盖雅是如何成為反派主角，以及史黛拉與好友們平常的互動。第一季在2015年1月24日結束。<ref>{{cite web|author1=RovioMobile|title=Angry Birds Stella 1 Ep.13 Sneak Peek - “To The Bitter End”|url=https://www.toons.tv/channels/Angry_Birds_Stella_S1/6a6a42539eab4a3d|accessdate=2015-02-28|date=January 24, 2015|quote="To The Bitter End" will be airing across all Angry Birds apps in the Angry Birds Toons channel and at http://toons.tv this Saturday, January 24!|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150323045627/https://www.toons.tv/channels/Angry_Birds_Stella_S1/6a6a42539eab4a3d|archivedate=2015-03-23|df=}}</ref>

